---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Hljóðver">
  <div class="page-hero">
    <div class="page-hero-left">
      <div class="eyebrow">Hönnun & framleiðsla</div>
      <h1>Hljóðver</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="page-hero-right">
      <p>Árið 2011 var útbúið fullkomið hljóðver og árið 2016 var svo bætt við öðru hljóðveri. Myndform hefur hljóðsett nokkrar vinsælustu teiknimyndir síðustu ára, auk þess hafa fjölmargar auglýsingar verið lesnar hér og hljóðblandaðar.</p>
      <a href="mailto:myndform@myndform.is" class="cta-btn">Hafðu samband</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="content">

    <div class="studio-section">
      <div class="studio-intro">
        <h2>Hljóðverið okkar</h2>
        <p>Við búum yfir tveimur faglegum hljóðverum með nýjasta búnað til upptöku, blöndunar og masteringar. Hljóðverin eru til leigu og við getum einnig aðstoðað við framleiðsluna.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="photo-grid">
        <div class="photo-item tall bg-studio-1">
          <div class="photo-label">Aðalhljóðver</div>
        </div>
        <div class="photo-item tall bg-studio-2">
          <div class="photo-label">Blöndunarpultar</div>
        </div>
        <div class="photo-item tall bg-studio-3">
          <div class="photo-label">Stjórnborð</div>
        </div>
        <div class="photo-item tall bg-studio-4">
          <div class="photo-label">Hljóðnemi</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-grid">
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-name">Upptökur</div>
        <div class="feature-desc">Raddar, þættir, auglýsingar og kvikmyndir — við tökum við öllum verkefnum.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-name">Blöndun & meðhöndlun</div>
        <div class="feature-desc">Fagleg hljóðblöndun og mastering fyrir hvaða miðil sem er.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-name">Kvikmyndahljóð</div>
        <div class="feature-desc">Hljóðlegar lausnir sérstaklega fyrir kvikmyndir og sjónvarpsefni.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-name">Útvarp & podcast</div>
        <div class="feature-desc">Tækni og aðstaða fyrir útvarpsdæmi og hlaðvarp í heimsmælikvarða.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="divider"></div>

    <div class="talsetning-section">
      <div class="talsetning-intro">
        <h2>Talsetning</h2>
        <p>Mikill fjöldi erlendra teiknimynda hafa verið talsettar hjá Myndform. Í samvinnu við framúrskarandi leikstjóra, ásamt stórskotaliði íslenskra leikara, hefur Myndform tekist að tryggja það að íslensk tunga sé alltaf til boða í skemmtiefni fyrir ungviði landsins.</p>
        <p>Vinsælar teiknimyndir sem Myndform hefur látið talsetja: Wicked, Aulinn ég, Skósveinarnir, Super Mario Bros Bíómyndin, Viana, Finding Dory, svo eitthvað sé nefnt.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="photo-grid">
        <div class="photo-item tall bg-film-1">
          <div class="photo-label">Skósveinarnir</div>
        </div>
        <div class="photo-item tall bg-film-2">
          <div class="photo-label">Syngdu 2</div>
        </div>
        <div class="photo-item tall bg-film-3">
          <div class="photo-label">Super Mario Bros</div>
        </div>
        <div class="photo-item tall bg-film-4">
          <div class="photo-label">Wicked</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="cta-strip">
    <div>
      <div class="cta-strip-title">Langar þig að bóka tíma?</div>
      <div class="cta-strip-sub">Hafðu samband og við finnum tíma sem hentar.</div>
    </div>
    <a href="mailto:myndform@myndform.is" class="cta-btn-red">Hafðu samband</a>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    background: #1a1a1d;
    padding: 56px 32px;
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 48px; align-items: center;
  }
  .eyebrow {
    font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: #ff5a5a; margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  h1 {
    font-size: 44px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--white);
    line-height: 1.05; letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }
  .page-hero-right p {
    font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
    line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .cta-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.85); color: var(--white);
    background: transparent; padding: 11px 22px; border-radius: 3px;
    font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase; text-decoration: none;
    transition: background 0.15s;
  }
  .cta-btn:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); }

  .content { padding: 48px 32px; }

  /* ── STUDIO SECTION ── */
  .studio-section { margin-bottom: 48px; }
  .studio-intro { margin-bottom: 28px; }
  .talsetning-intro { margin-bottom: 28px; }

  h2 {
    font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .studio-intro p,
  .talsetning-intro p {
    font-size: 14px; color: var(--gray-60); line-height: 1.75;
    max-width: 640px; margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  /* ── PHOTO GRID ── */
  .photo-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 8px;
  }
  .photo-item {
    aspect-ratio: 4/3; border-radius: 6px;
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  .photo-label {
    position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    padding: 28px 14px 12px;
    background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(0,0,0,0.7) 0%, transparent 100%);
    font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; color: #fff;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em; text-transform: uppercase;
    opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.2s;
  }
  .photo-item:hover .photo-label { opacity: 1; }

  /* studio photo placeholder colours */
  .bg-studio-1 { background: linear-gradient(145deg, #1a1a2e, #16213e); }
  .bg-studio-2 { background: linear-gradient(145deg, #2a2a2a, #1a1a1a); }
  .bg-studio-3 { background: linear-gradient(145deg, #1e2a1e, #111811); }
  .bg-studio-4 { background: linear-gradient(145deg, #2a1a1a, #1a1010); }

  /* film poster placeholder colours */
  .bg-film-1 { background: linear-gradient(145deg, #f59e0b, #d97706); }
  .bg-film-2 { background: linear-gradient(145deg, #3b82f6, #1d4ed8); }
  .bg-film-3 { background: linear-gradient(145deg, #ef4444, #b91c1c); }
  .bg-film-4 { background: linear-gradient(145deg, #10b981, #047857); }

  /* ── FEATURES ── */
  .feature-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 48px;
  }
  .feature-card {
    background: var(--gray-10);
    border-radius: 8px; padding: 24px;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--red);
  }
  .feature-name { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .feature-desc { font-size: 13px; color: var(--gray-60); line-height: 1.6; }

  .divider { height: 1px; background: var(--gray-20); margin-bottom: 48px; }

  .talsetning-section { margin-bottom: 0; }

  /* ── CTA ── */
  .cta-strip {
    margin: 48px 32px;
    background: var(--gray-10); border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 28px 32px;
    display: flex; align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between; gap: 24px;
  }
  .cta-strip-title { font-size: 17px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .cta-strip-sub { font-size: 13px; color: var(--gray-60); }
  .cta-btn-red {
    display: inline-block;
    border: 2px solid var(--red); color: var(--red);
    background: transparent; padding: 11px 22px; border-radius: 3px;
    font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase; text-decoration: none; white-space: nowrap;
    transition: background 0.15s, color 0.15s;
  }
  .cta-btn-red:hover { background: var(--red); color: var(--white); }

  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    .page-hero { grid-template-columns: 1fr; padding: 48px 20px; }
    h1 { font-size: 32px; }
    .photo-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    .feature-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    .cta-strip { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; margin: 32px 20px; }
  }
</style>